# bb-auth access allowlist — one email per line. '#' starts a comment.
# This is the REAL access gate (Cognito self-signup is open). Re-checked on every
# /auth/validate, so removing a line + `systemctl reload bb-auth` (SIGHUP) denies
# even existing sessions; a plain restart works too. Emails are matched
# case-insensitively.
you@example.com
friend@example.com
